{
  "stem": "19939.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 116.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no right for a passport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the time, they-- so I have to mention about this uncle, that he survived the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a, a soldier in the First World War in Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they took him 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somehow, he was a prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was not aware of what, what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I found a letter addressed to his family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They want him come now, my dears, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he met some of the Polish neighbors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they told him that I escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he started looking for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He went to this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the people there where it was-- I don't know how he did it-- they gave him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he traced Lambert.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he traced me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this Lambert sent him back a telegram.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the time-- and so he was-- there were pogroms in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know that he sold the-- his house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, they were well-off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He found some cash or dollars in the something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he had money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was able to, you know, come with a passport to Paris.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I could never go-- had no, no passport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only way was to repatriate to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they started to repatriate the Polish people to Poland or to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Russians didn't want to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took my things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to the train with other people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I took my books, whatever I had, some possessions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, I just-- the fear of being Jewish in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am repeating this, because the, the, the emotional scar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It never left me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It never left me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
